author: David R. Baker
title: Tesla: News crew tried to run over Gigafactory guards
text:
Photo: Tesla Motors Tesla's rendering of the Gigafactory, currently under construction east of Reno, Nevada. Tesla's rendering of the Gigafactory, currently under construction...
Such is the public fascination with the Tesla Motors Gigafactory that the $5 billion battery plant taking shape in the Nevada desert may have had what amounts to a run-in with the paparazzi last week.
